        <body>
      
		<pb n="1"/>
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>San Francisco</placeName> <date>Nov 3 of 54</date></p>
			<p><addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(3)">Dear Friend&#8212;</p>
          <p rend="indent(5)">I take<lb/> great Pleasure in informing you&#44;<lb/> that after many Runs&#44; Exertions and<lb/> all other numerous little difficulties<lb/> attendant upon collecting from men who<lb/> are opposed to the Idea &#8220;to pay up&#44;&#8221; that<lb/> I have succeeded in collecting to&#45;day<lb/> &#36;24&#8212; from <persName>R. Schoya</persName> for 8 years<lb/> subscription to the Occident&#59; for this I<lb/> ask some little Credit from you&#44; as I<lb/> do not believe any one else could have<lb/> pumped it out of him&#44; acknowledge<lb/> the Receipt thereof&#8212; I would indeed<lb/> like very much to send you some money&#44;<lb/> but your account now stands yet about<lb/> &#36;20&#8212; overdrawn&#44; as last time I remitted<lb/> much beyond the funds I <sic>haad</sic> on hand<lb/> for you&#59; besides I did not yet succeed<lb/> in collecting the Sunday&#45;School Books Bill.<lb/> To&#45;day I have also collected from <persName>Mr<lb/> Henry Seligman</persName> &#36;11.86&#47;100 for advertising<lb/> in the Occident&#44; all of which I have taken<lb/> in for you&#44; I have placed to your Credit&#59;</p>
		<pb n="2"/>
			<p>and you will acknowledge also Receipt for<lb/> the latter amt. I have paid <persName>Spat &#38; Ten&#45;<lb/>&#45;house</persName> &#36;23 35&#47;100 for Freight &#38;c for the<lb/> sunday school Books what in also another<lb/> Item to help to overdraw.</p>
			<p>Enclosed I hand you an article which I<lb/> cut out from the &#8220;Herald&#8221; of this city of<lb/> <persName>Mr. Qo</persName>&#44; which may perhaps be of some<lb/> service to you in as much as it may<lb/> throw some further light in what<lb/> is hitherto known of the Jews in <placeName>China</placeName>&#59;<lb/> I have no Doubt&#44; that Jews exist in<lb/> <placeName>China</placeName>.</p>
			<p>I regret exceedingly&#44; that I cannot<lb/> this time inform you of something in&#45;<lb/>&#45;teresting for the Occident.</p>
			<p>In conclusion I beg you to accept<lb/> my best wishes for your welfare &#38;<lb/> Prosperity</p>
          <p rend="indent(9)">whilst I Remain</p>
          <p rend="indent(10)">your true friend</p>
          <p rend="indent(9)"><persName role="author">Cauffman H Meyer</persName></p>
          
        </body>
